                        <persName xml:lang="ar">الشهاني عبد الرزاق</persName>
                     </author>
                     <title xml:lang="ar-Latn-x-lc" key="work_7654">Sharḥ al-risālah</title>
                     <note>Commentary on <title xml:lang="ar-Latn-x-lc">Risālat al-Qushayrī <foreign xml:lang="ar">رسالة القشيري</foreign>
                        </title> by <persName key="person_68980610" ref="http://viaf.org/viaf/68980610" xml:lang="ar-Latn-x-lc" type="standard">Qushayrī, ʿAbd al-Karīm ibn Hawāzin, 986-1072 <foreign xml:lang="ar">القشيري، عبد الكريم بن هوازن، 376-465 هـ</foreign>
                        </persName>
                     </note>
                     <note>The MS contains only the first part of Qushayrī's work; beginning as well as title and author's name missing. The commentary is generally short, and th emajor part of the MS is often occupied with Qushayrī's text itself. The colophon, where the name of the commentar is found is on <locus from="184b" to="184b">fol. 184v</locus>.</note>
                     <incipit xml:lang="ar"/>
                     <explicit xml:lang="fa" defective="inapplicable">تم الجزء الاول من شرح الرسالة باسم مولانا الشيخ ... الشهاني عبد الرزاق</explicit>
                     <note>
